fields.name: Signature Bobble Hat - Blue
fields.description: Keep your ears covered from the cold winter wind in between sessions, while changing or relaxing on the beach or a café patio in this super warm woolly hat. All beanies are handmade in Wales by Seafoam founder Stien, knit using 100% Peruvian Highland Wool. The non-itchy, high quality, chunky wool will keep you warm, that's for sure!

fields.name: Hossegor Headband - Mauve
fields.description: The perfect companion for colder days. Keep your ears covered from the cold wind while changing or relaxing on the beach or a café patio. Headbands are great if you like to wear your hair in a pony tail or bun, without getting chilly ears. All headbands are handmade in Wales by Seafoam founder Stien, using 100% Peruvian Highland Wool. This great quality wool is non itchy and will keep your ears nice and warm.
